{"tid":541953,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖討論] 由你親自打造一隊四代女團，你會點揀？","createTime":"2018-01-27T04:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T09:36:41.000Z","uid":155084,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"aed46e494c0b46d7e4c2055e3f247a6ebe8c30ad","tid":541953,"uid":155084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T04:21:57.000Z","msg":"認真討論！<br />\n<br />\n假設你係比三大經紀次一級嘅中型經紀公司老闆，依家你有一筆大資金，可以用黎招兵買馬，組成一隊女團推出市場。你嘅選擇係 ...?<br />\n<br />\n女團成員規限 : <br />\n1.女團風格定位不限<br />\n2.女團成員人數上限為12人<br />\n3.女團成員不限，但外國人成員不能多於韓國人成員<br />\n4.女團成員出生年份須為 1988~2003年 之間<br />\n<br />\n麻煩巴絲講你既組合時，簡介兩句講下風格定位，<br />\n同埋註明每位成員在隊內的職務（每成員最少一項）。<br />\n<br />\n最好有埋圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全韓國人，7人女團 <br />\n<br />\n孝定 - 隊長、副唱 (94,原Oh My Girl)<br />\n銀河 - 主唱 (97,原Gfriend)<br />\nSinB - 主領舞 (98,原Gfriend)<br />\nUmji - 副唱 (98,原Gfriend)<br />\nNC.A - 副唱 (96,原Solo)<br />\n多榮 - 副唱 (99,原宇宙少女）<br />\n美娜 - 忙內、副領舞、主Rapper (99,原gugudan)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定位： 一隊具歌唱實力，形象正面清純，曲風輕快有力，混合出&quot;力量清純&quot;的全韓國人7人女團。<br />\n<br />\n孝定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/120857_17e0a5c4ea1297c93016677e1fc72848.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F120857_17e0a5c4ea1297c93016677e1fc72848.jpeg&h=0756a8fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/120858_b471457504ce8c123bcc6d38d8608ed4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F120858_b471457504ce8c123bcc6d38d8608ed4.jpeg&h=702250d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/120859_8a021eed631ce435d21ae7c4096d6abf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F120859